---
title: Chicken and Braised Cabbage with Garlic Mash and Dill Cream
description: On those chilly spring evenings you just want to tuck into a dish that'll warm you inside and out! What could do that better than fragrant roasted chicken breasts atop braised red cabbage and apple, with a pile of creamy, garlicky mashed potatoes alongside!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-et-chou-braise-a5ce76e3.jpg
